{"lastModified":1768299271906,"uri":"c::8164602117::vessel::dabc4520-ed55-11f0-9b8a-471ca0fd6a08","yachtType":["Sailing","Gulet"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nCan you imagine the perfect blend of relaxation, adventure and hidden treasures? Step aboard Belgin Sultan and let the turquoise Mediterranean set the rhythm of your journey. \n\nCruising at a gentle 11 knots, life on deck feels effortless. Sunbathe, relax in the Jacuzzi or dive into the sea with kayaks, paddleboards and more. Inside, elegant spaces and warm service make you feel instantly at home. Outside, handpicked routes lead you from ancient ruins to charming coastal towns waiting to be explored.\n\nPerfect for couples, families and small groups, Belgin Sultan offers a refined blue‐cruise experience without the luxury price tag. Personal, relaxed and full of authentic moments you’ll remember long after you return. This is where that perfect mix becomes real.\n\nTHE SPIRIT OF THE SOUTH\nCruising in Türkiye combines ancient history, sparkling blue  seas, and a warm, vibrant culture. As you sail along the Aegean and Mediterranean coasts, you can explore archaeological treasures, unwind on secluded beaches, and savor the rich flavors of Turkish cuisine. Traditional wooden gulets, many of them carefully renewed, offer a comfortable and authentic way to experience the coast. Since these iconic vessels originate here, the journey feels even more genuine and memorable.","blueprint":{"name":"BELGIN SULTAN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::dabc4520-ed55-11f0-9b8a-471ca0fd6a08::assets::6468f370-ed58-11f0-b0e1-67a39b98eed0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dabc4520-ed55-11f0-9b8a-471ca0fd6a08::assets::646e4aa0-ed58-11f0-b0e2-67a39b98eed0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dabc4520-ed55-11f0-9b8a-471ca0fd6a08::assets::646d3931-ed58-11f0-b0e2-67a39b98eed0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dabc4520-ed55-11f0-9b8a-471ca0fd6a08::assets::647b6a00-ed58-11f0-8